*IIće* se da će biti hladan večer (It is expected that it will be a cold evening). 

Uvek se *ii* slagao sa svojim roditeljima (He always got along with his parents). 

Ona je *iila* u školu da bi se obrazovala (She went to school to get educated). 

*Išli* su učiti kako da plivaju (They went to learn how to swim). 

On je *iio* u prodavnicu da kupi sladoled (He went to the store to buy ice cream).